FBIS4-15835 "drsov070_u_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-070 Daily Report 11 Apr 1994 Latvia Commander: Withdrawal on Schedule Commander: Withdrawal on Schedule LD1104163994 Riga Radio Riga Network in Latvian 1500 GMT 11 Apr 94 LD1104163994 Riga Radio Riga Network Latvian BFN [Text] Latvian Defense Minister Valdis Pavlovskis and Ilgonis Upmalis, head of the Latvian bureau for monitoring the withdrawal of the Russian Army, today met Leonid Mayorov, supreme commander of the Northwestern Group of Russian forces, to discuss problems related to the withdrawal. Mayorov told the Latvian officials that the withdrawal of troops and Army property was proceeding according to schedule, coordinating it with the progress of housing construction in Russia.
